Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Kansas City
Description: A metropolitan city in the Midwest that I will always call home. Located on the state line between Missouri and Kansas; however, the majority of the city resides in Missouri.

Name: Santa Cruz
Description: A beach town in northern California. (I spent two years here in my undergrad and one day hope to take my parents. Santa Cruz beaches are superior!)

Name: New York City
Description: A heavily populared city with rich history and culture. (A life goal of mine is to live in this city for at least a year and see where it takes me.)

Name: Nelson Atkins Museum of Art
Description: An art museum located in Kansas City, MO known for its extensive collection of Asian art with an aesthetic coffee shop and sculpture garden.
